Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.83,1:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妳吸呀
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.56,1:11:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.59,1:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊\N覆蓋全身的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.23,1:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這種快感\N是我從來沒有體験過的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.49,1:11:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,給我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.24,1:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
