Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.55,1:28:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你盡情的撫摸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.75,1:29:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快呀
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.85,1:29:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.87,1:29:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我想吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.61,1:29:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你吞下去呀
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.61,1:29:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你全部都吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.68,1:29:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要吃了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.28,1:30:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.02,1:30:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.75,1:30:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.35,1:31:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  我要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.47,1:31:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妳很爽快對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.74,1:31:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽快的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.37,1:31:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  我要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.14,1:31:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可以呀  妳盡情的去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.44,1:32:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.37,1:32:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妳自己撐開給我看看呀
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.11,1:32:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,請你看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.88,1:32:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看得很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.49,1:32:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你盡情的看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.62,1:32:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妳那裡想我舔的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.59,1:32:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.11,1:33:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在我融化之前\N你盡情的舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.21,1:33:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在妳融化之前呀
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.60,1:33:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,超爽快的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.41,1:33:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.04,1:33:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.78,1:33:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.85,1:33:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續  繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.33,1:34:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,繼績
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.51,1:34:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.14,1:34:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.23,1:34:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.20,1:34:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,妳很濕了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.31,1:34:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.85,1:34:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.16,1:35:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒呀
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.70,1:35:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.42,1:35:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.35,1:35:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.19,1:35:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.43,1:35:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.10,1:35:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.87,1:35:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.71,1:35:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續啊\N繼縉是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.35,1:35:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.02,1:36:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.72,1:36:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了  要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.15,1:36:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可以呀\N我要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.52,1:36:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.65,1:36:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,來呀
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.92,1:36:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在妳的後背\N是什麼頂到妳啦?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.86,1:36:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是爸爸健壯的東西  頂到我了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.17,1:36:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,健壯的什麼呀?\N妳說清楚呀
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.11,1:37:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是健壯的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.72,1:37:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,頂到我了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.79,1:37:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妳很討厭的吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.96,1:37:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.13,1:37:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜歡好喜歡\N我都受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.32,1:37:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.50,1:38:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以隨妳喜歡喔
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.24,1:39:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你爽快嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.21,1:39:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,超爽快的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.18,1:39:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.23,1:40:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妳想要這個的吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.43,1:40:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.48,1:41:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,說妳想要呀
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.45,1:41:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.92,1:41:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要這個
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.06,1:41:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,給我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.71,1:41:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妳自己握住
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.71,1:41:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妳來插入呀
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.98,1:42:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.62,1:42:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.99,1:42:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.86,1:42:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.49,1:42:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.38,1:42:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒喔  太淫蕩了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.01,1:42:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好好的感受吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.99,1:42:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我從下面給妳抽動吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.13,1:42:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.13,1:42:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.04,1:43:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.45,1:43:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以呀
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.52,1:43:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.79,1:43:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊  爸爸\N好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.13,1:43:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒很爽快吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.26,1:44:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妳把腿打開呀
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.27,1:44:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.67,1:44:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看到吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.94,1:44:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸的肉棒  在插入
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.88,1:44:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.39,1:45:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.20,1:45:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.29,1:45:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽快呀
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.31,1:45:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.77,1:46:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你用力抽動啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.31,1:46:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我又要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.78,1:46:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.54,1:46:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我又要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.81,1:47:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,妳去呀
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.78,1:47:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.96,1:47:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害呀  繼續來做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.13,1:47:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,將妳的屁股轉過來呀
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.03,1:47:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,頂中了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.76,1:48:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.94,1:49:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.88,1:49:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.13,1:49:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.76,1:49:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.09,1:50:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.27,1:50:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是這裡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.24,1:50:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.31,1:50:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.36,1:51:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,妳過來這邊呀
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.45,1:51:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.85,1:51:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.42,1:51:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.00,1:51:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽快吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.08,1:52:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以喔  妳不要動
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.58,1:52:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為太爽快了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.42,1:52:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒這麼大
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.96,1:52:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快呀
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.50,1:52:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想鬆開
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.47,1:52:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽快吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.34,1:52:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我也無法忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.81,1:52:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想繼續感受  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.89,1:52:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽快呢
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.63,1:52:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.74,1:53:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.11,1:53:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.38,1:53:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.42,1:53:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.10,1:54:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,妳起來呀
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.40,1:55:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是過分的老爸呀
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.27,1:55:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.57,1:55:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不過作為男人  作為雄性
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.15,1:56:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你擁有著渴望女性的本性
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.33,1:56:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,奈美  不久前妳在電話裡面\N聽說了我父親的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.84,1:56:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼突然提這個呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.32,1:56:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之後  我也反省了一下
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.62,1:56:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我給保險公司打電話了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.19,1:56:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然後呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.60,1:56:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然後保險公司說\N你們和好了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.84,1:57:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道對方在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.41,1:57:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你指什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.55,1:57:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸甚至都不知道我們結婚了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.59,1:57:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他卻重新買了一份壽險
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.17,1:57:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,受保人是奈美妳
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.34,1:57:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎麼知道的呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.15,1:57:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我太混亂了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.32,1:57:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我\N我也想變得積極一點了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.43,1:57:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣呀
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.87,1:58:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想見見他呢
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.92,1:58:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（縛演昇天城）
